| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5805 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 20ef6aed-b53f-576f-b0b7-4fd4f8425dd1"
